{"id":321097,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/11/【组图】山西省委门口今晨发生连环爆炸-疑似自制/","date":"2013-11-06T01:57:26Z","modified":"2017-01-29T20:05:25Z","title":"【组图】山西省委门口今晨发生连环爆炸 系自制炸弹","content":"<p>11月6日早晨，山西太原市迎泽大街，山西省委门口发生连环爆炸，约有七八声巨响。据悉，事先埋藏在省委门口花丛中的爆炸物发生爆炸，致使多辆汽车受损，官方称目前已有1人死亡、1人重伤、7人轻伤。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-321097 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/11/%e3%80%90%e7%bb%84%e5%9b%be%e3%80%91%e5%b1%b1%e8%a5%bf%e7%9c%81%e5%a7%94%e9%97%a8%e5%8f%a3%e4%bb%8a%e6%99%a8%e5%8f%91%e7%94%9f%e8%bf%9e%e7%8e%af%e7%88%86%e7%82%b8-%e7%96%91%e4%bc%bc%e8%87%aa%e5%88%b6/698517c6jw1eaaytaytx4j20qo0f0jst/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/698517c6jw1eaaytaytx4j20qo0f0jst-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/698517c6jw1eaaytaytx4j20qo0f0jst-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/698517c6jw1eaaytaytx4j20qo0f0jst-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/11/%e3%80%90%e7%bb%84%e5%9b%be%e3%80%91%e5%b1%b1%e8%a5%bf%e7%9c%81%e5%a7%94%e9%97%a8%e5%8f%a3%e4%bb%8a%e6%99%a8%e5%8f%91%e7%94%9f%e8%bf%9e%e7%8e%af%e7%88%86%e7%82%b8-%e7%96%91%e4%bc%bc%